msgstr "版本"

msgid ""
"A simple banner grabber which connects to an open TCP port and prints out "
"anything sent by the listening service within five seconds."
msgstr ""
"一个简单的横幅抓取器，连接到开放的TCP端口并打印出监听服务在五秒内发送的任何内容。横幅将被截断为单行，但每增加一个详细级别可额外打印一行。"

msgid "Shows the title of the default page of a web server."
msgstr "显示Web服务器默认页面的标题。"

msgid "Shows SSH hostkeys."
msgstr "显示SSH主机密钥。"

msgid ""
"Retrieves information from a listening acarsd daemon. Acarsd decodes\n"
"ACARS (Aircraft Communication Addressing and Reporting System) data in\n"
"real time.  The information retrieved by this script includes the\n"
"daemon version, API version, administrator e-mail address and\n"
"listening frequency."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Shows extra information about IPv6 addresses, such as embedded MAC or IPv4 "
"addresses when available."
msgstr ""

msgid "Performs password guessing against Apple Filing Protocol (AFP)."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Attempts to get useful information about files from AFP volumes.\n"
"The output is intended to resemble the output of <code>ls</code>."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Detects the Mac OS X AFP directory traversal vulnerability, CVE-2010-0533."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Shows AFP server information. This information includes the server's\n"
"hostname, IPv4 and IPv6 addresses, and hardware type (for example\n"
